description:
AJKM-02 EMBROIDERED POLY COTTON 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Poly Cotton Trouser: Poly Cotton Dupatta: Chiffon Color: Purple

Mawra Hocane looks resplendent garbed in this elegant attire.Deep shade of plum is encrusted by heavy thread work with a touch of spangles making this design a coveted addition to your wardrobe. It comes with chiffon dupatta trimmed with embroidered borders & same hued pants.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered Center Panel On Silk
Embroidered Right Panel On Silk
Embroidered Left Panel On Silk
30'' Embroidered Border For Front Daman On Silk
30'' Dyed Wide Width Silk For Back
30'' Embroidered Border For Back Daman On Silk
Embroidered Sleeves With Border On Silk
2.5 Meter Embroidered Dupatta On Chiffon
1.5 Meter Dyed Wide Width Silk For Trouser
